                United States. Let B1 be the event that
                <?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T154530-0500" content="the first person"?><?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T154530-0500"?>one
                of the people<?oxy_insert_end?> has blue eyes and B2 be the event that the
                <?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T154542-0500"?>other<?oxy_insert_end?><?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T154543-0500" content="second"?>
                person has blue eyes. In this case, since
