                and therefore B1 and B2 are independent. On the other hand<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T154218-0500"?>
                <?oxy_insert_end?>...<?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101108T154221-0500" content=".."?><?oxy_comment_end?></p>
